title: #92Noon! Montage/Vikings/Bercich/Lavelle
description: The morning montage is a funky one after the Vikings win 28-12 in the season opener. A ton of Vikings and NFL nuggets throughout the show including Pete Bercich in studio late in the first hour. Lavelle is in studio most of the final stretch on Twins and football, with calls to close!
